{"tid":2214473,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"手足又輸。手足決定撤銷太古城一家三口限聚令無理檢控","createTime":"2020-09-23T09:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T08:53:31.000Z","uid":273218,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"886a412329fc94e000bb5e6c734645f443131f70","tid":2214473,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:28:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=190063759150117&amp;id=100556368100857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D190063759150117%26id%3D100556368100857&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9obCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=4e565241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=190063759150117&amp;id=100556368100857</a><br />\n<br />\n今年母親節，警方以限聚令為由進入太古城中心商場，趙博一直在場監察警方行動，並目睹有一家三口加一途人被控違反當時上限8人之「#限聚令」。縱使前線警員無法解釋票控理據，但仍堅持發出告票，#DrAndrew 隨後協助事主一家草擬抗辯信要求撤銷檢控。近日獲事主告知，警方決定撤銷對其一家三口的無理檢控，#成功透過書面抗辯討回公道。<br />\n<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f50bda0658c4c7d6f98d294f4174fa2e753711","tid":2214473,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:29:34.000Z","msg":"前線手足唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd2aedc7d0cc0987bcc3bf6e007466f9e84b39a","tid":2214473,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55f50bda0658c4c7d6f98d294f4174fa2e753711","tid":2214473,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:29:34.000Z","msg":"前線手足唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"